## Environment Separation

### Workspace vs Directory Strategy

| Strategy | Use When | Example |
|----------|----------|---------|
| Directory per environment | Different configs, clear isolation | environments/dev, environments/prod |
| Workspace per environment | Same config, different state | terraform workspace select prod |
| Separate repos | Strict compliance boundaries | infra-dev repo, infra-prod repo |

### Environment Promotion Checklist

- [ ] Same IaC code promotes through environments (no environment-specific branches)
- [ ] Differences are parameterized via tfvars or workspace variables
- [ ] Production state is separate and access-controlled
- [ ] Promotion requires approval (manual or automated gate)

### Variable Per Environment

```hcl
# environments/prod/terraform.tfvars
environment = "prod"
instance_count = 6
instance_type = "m5.xlarge"
enable_backup = true
```

