## Naming Conventions

### Resource Naming

| Resource Type | Pattern | Example |
|--------------|---------|---------|
| General | {project}-{env}-{component}-{resource} | myapp-prod-api-ec2 |
| Short IDs | {project}-{env}-{component} | myapp-prod-db |
| VPC/Network | {project}-{env}-vpc | myapp-prod-vpc |

### Tagging Standards

| Tag | Required | Values | Purpose |
|-----|----------|--------|---------|
| Environment | Yes | dev, staging, prod | Filtering, cost allocation |
| Project | Yes | Project name | Cost center, ownership |
| Owner | Yes | Team or email | Incident contact |
| ManagedBy | Yes | terraform, pulumi | Indicates IaC-managed |
| CostCenter | Recommended | Finance code | Chargeback |

### Tag Enforcement

```hcl
# Use policy or validation to enforce tags
variable "required_tags" {
  type = map(string)
  default = {
    Environment = "prod"
    Project     = "myapp"
    Owner       = "platform-team"
    ManagedBy   = "terraform"
  }
}
```

